## âš™ï¸ Model Training Workflow

1. Load the dataset  
2. Separate features and target variable  
3. Perform stratified train-test split  
4. Apply feature scaling using StandardScaler  
5. Balance training data using SMOTE  
6. Train Extra Trees Classifier  
7. Evaluate model using classification metrics  
8. Save trained model and scaler  

---

## ğŸ“Š Model Evaluation Metrics

- Accuracy  
- Precision  
- **Recall (Primary Focus)**  
- F1-Score  
- ROC-AUC  
- Confusion Matrix  

> **Recall is prioritized** because missing a fraudulent transaction is more costly than incorrectly flagging a genuine one.

